title: Dartmouth, River Dart and Dartmoor in 1910 in Colour! [HD enhanced & AI colorized]

sources.title: Dartmouth, River Dart and Dartmoor in 1910 in Colour! [HD enhanced & AI colorized]
sources.description: A very short film about Dartmouth, the River Dart and Dartmoor over a century ago in 1910. Dartmouth is a Civil Parish in the south west of the United Kingdom in the district South Hams in the county of Devon. Dartmouth lies near an estuary where also Dartmouth castle can be found. This castle can also be seen in this film. The town dates from the middle ages. This film has been motion-stabilized, speed-corrected, restored and colorized with modern Artificial Intelligence software. Timeline: 00:00 Dartmouth High Street 00:13 River Dart 00:26 Steps up from the river
